<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Status Update - Smile Sync</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .notification-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 500px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #721c24;
        background-color: #f8d7da;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 26px;
      }
      .important-note {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #856404;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .info {
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        background-color: #6c757d;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #5a6268;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
      }
      .warning-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        color: #dc3545;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="notification-container">
      <div class="warning-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>Account Suspension Notice</h1>
      <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
      <p>
        We regret to inform you that your Smile Sync account has been suspended due to violations of our Terms of Service.
      </p>
      
      <div class="important-note">
        Reason: <%= banReason %>
      </div>
      
      <p class="info">
        Our system has detected activities that are not permitted under our platform's guidelines. After careful review, our moderation team has determined that this action is necessary to maintain a safe and professional environment for all users.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        As a result of this suspension:
      </p>
      <ul style="text-align: left; color: #555;">
        <li>You can no longer access your account</li>
        <li>Any upcoming appointments have been canceled</li>
        <li>You cannot create new accounts with our service</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        If you believe this action was taken in error, you may appeal this decision by contacting our support team.
      </p>
      
      <a href="mailto:support@smilesync.com?subject=Account Suspension Appeal" class="btn">Contact Support</a>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p>The Smile Sync Safety Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>